        <p class="text-xs text-text-muted"><span class="highlight">Strengths:</span> ChatGPT tested as standard in every audit. Understands the Bing-ChatGPT pipeline. Original research data on ChatGPT recommendation patterns. Transparent pricing from GBP 800/mo.</p>
        <p class="text-xs text-text-muted mt-1">rank4ai.co.uk</p>
