      <p class="text-sm text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-3">Most SEO agencies optimise for Google. ChatGPT uses Bing. That single difference changes which signals matter. Your Bing Places listing, your Bing Webmaster Tools setup, your IndexNow implementation, your structured data that Bing specifically supports - these all feed into whether ChatGPT can find and recommend your business.</p>
      <p class="text-sm text-text-muted leading-relaxed">Beyond the Bing pipeline, ChatGPT also relies on its training data and browsing capability. Content clarity, entity consistency across the web, and authoritative citations all influence how ChatGPT talks about your brand. A good ChatGPT SEO agency understands all three layers.</p>
